    "thoughts": {
        "text": "Adding more diverse and surprising facts from various scientific fields to enrich the list. The facts are still being extracted from the Science Focus website.",
        "reasoning": "Continuing to compile a comprehensive list of scientific facts to ensure a varied and interesting collection. The chosen facts are not only diverse but each brings a unique aspect of science to the user's attention.",
        "plan": "- Keep appending more facts to 'interesting_science_facts.txt'\n- Ensure variety and interest level in facts chosen\n- Once compilation seems adequate, start ranking them\n- Prioritize sending the completed and ranked list with proper citations",
        "criticism": "The append process is repetitive but necessary due to memory constraints. There may be a more optimal way to rate or qualify the 'interestingness' of facts, which will be explored in the ranking process.",
        "summaryforgpt": "Further appended diverse facts to 'interesting_science_facts.txt'. The process will persist until an adequate number of facts are compiled. The next steps involve ranking these facts and then communicating them to the user."
    }
