        "name": "message_user",
        "args": {
            "message": "Here is the ranked list of interesting science facts based on uniqueness and the potential to captivate interest, starting with the most intriguing:\n\n1. Earth’s poles are moving, which could potentially cause a magnetic reversal. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n2. The Universe’s average colour is ‘Cosmic latte’. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n3. Chainsaws were first invented for childbirth, not for woodchopping. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n4. All the world’s bacteria stacked on top of each other would stretch for 10 billion light-years. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n5. The human brain undergoes ‘phagocytosis’, eating itself to remove dead and weak cells. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n6. Giraffes are 30 times more likely to get hit by lightning than people. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n7. A chicken lived for 18 months without a head in the 1940s. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n8. Octopuses don’t actually have tentacles, they are arms. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n9. NASA faked part of the Moon landing protocols for astronaut quarantine. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n10. The T.rex likely had feathers. Source: https://www.sciencefocus.com/science/fun-facts\n\nPlease let me know if you need more information or further assistance.",
            "wait_for_response": "False"
        }
    },
    "thoughts": {
        "text": "I have ranked the facts based on my assessment of their uniqueness and potential to captivate interest.",
        "reasoning": "The ranking is based on the criteria that include the rarity of the fact, its surprise factor, and its potential to elicit a 'wow' response. Facts that challenge common perceptions or are counterintuitive were given higher ranks.",
        "plan": "- Provide the user with the ranked list\n- Wait for any further instructions or requests from the user",
